description: Try our easy to follow Salmon & Spinach Lasagne recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Salmon & Spinach Lasagne Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Spread 1/4 of the sauce over the base of dish. Top with 1/3 of pasta. Spread over half of the seafood mixture. Repeat layers. Finish with remaining sauce and parmesan. Bake for 40 minutes until golden.
